Single.Single: ExecuteMove: BOOL; // Execute a step and direction incremental move
Steps: UDINT := 3000; // Number of motor pulses for incremental move
ResetAlarmOutput: BOOL; // Reset alarm output to motor controller
SpeedOutput: UINT; // Analog speed output to motor controller
Complete: BOOL; // Pulses TRUE when a move command has completed
InputFunction: UINT; // High speed counter setting, 1 = Simple Count
CounterLimit: UDINT; // High speed counter maximum count
RateChannel: UINT; // High speed counter window = 1
RateTime: UINT; // High speed counter rate time in milliseconds = 1000
CounterCommand: UINT; // High speed counter command 0 = Keep Counting, 1 = Stop Counting, 2 = Clear Count
